OL,5, Amazon could soon be forced to         
OL,6, recognise a trade union in the UK for  
OL,7, the first time.                        
OL,9,FThe GMB union says it has enrolled a   
OL,10,Fmajority of workers at Amazon's        
OL,11,FCoventry warehouse which qualifies them
OL,12,Ffor recognition by law.                
OL,14,FIt has written to the company asking to
OL,15,Fbe recognised.                         
OL,17,FAmazon says it "respects its employees'
OL,18,Frights to choose to join or not join a 
OL,19,Flabour union".                         
